### Start a workout session from a template
POST http://localhost:3000/sessions/start/1
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### Get my sessions
GET http://localhost:3000/sessions/mine

###

### Get a specific session by id
GET http://localhost:3000/sessions/1

###

### Update a session
PATCH http://localhost:3000/sessions/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Updated session notes",
  "performedAt": "2026-03-11T18:00:00.000Z"
}

###

### Create a set for an incomplete session
POST http://localhost:3000/sessions/1/sets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionExerciseId": 1,
  "order": 1,
  "reps": 8,
  "weight": 100,
  "rpe": 8,
  "rir": 2,
  "notes": "Felt good"
}

###

### Complete a session
POST http://localhost:3000/sessions/1/complete

###

### Try completing the same session again
POST http://localhost:3000/sessions/1/complete

###

### Verify completed session via GET
GET http://localhost:3000/sessions/1

###

### Try updating a completed session
PATCH http://localhost:3000/sessions/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "This should fail because the session is completed"
}

###

### Try creating a set for a completed session
POST http://localhost:3000/sessions/1/sets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionExerciseId": 1,
  "order": 2,
  "reps": 10,
  "weight": 105
}

###

### Try updating a set on a completed session
PATCH http://localhost:3000/sessions/sets/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reps": 9
}

###

### Try deleting a set on a completed session
DELETE http://localhost:3000/sessions/sets/1

###

### Delete a session
DELETE http://localhost:3000/sessions/1

###

### Update a set
PATCH http://localhost:3000/sessions/sets/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reps": 9,
  "weight": 102.5,
  "notes": "Last set, pushed harder"
}

###

### Clear optional set fields
PATCH http://localhost:3000/sessions/sets/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rpe": "",
  "rir": "",
  "notes": ""
}

###

### Delete a set
DELETE http://localhost:3000/sessions/sets/1